            "pub_date": "2026-01-29 11:14:25",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6325719,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 基士德-KY(6641)急拉3.51%報23.05元，成交94張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>基士德-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6641:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6641\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6641-TW</a>)近5分K漲速3.51%，29日11:14報23.05元，成交94張，今日跌幅為1.5％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>基士德-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6641:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6641\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6641-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.89%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+2 張</li> <li>融資增減：-5 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
